": "wait", "image": "static/manifest/data/task2-gpt5.4-mini-sample-3/21.webp", "action_value_1": []}, {"id": 21, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/task2-gpt5.4-mini-sample-3/22.webp", "action_value_1": "EOF", "thought": "刚才的 here-doc 似乎没有完整结束，终端还在等待结束标记。我先补上 `EOF` 关闭当前输入，再重新用更稳妥的短命令创建完整模型文件。"}, {"id": 22, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/task2-gpt5.4-mini-sample-3/23.webp", "action_value_1": "python3 -c ", "thought": "我已经退出刚才的错误输入状态。现在改用单行 `python3 -c` 直接写文件，避免 here-doc 再次被截断。这样更稳，也更适合在 GUI 环境里操作。"}, {"id": 23, "action_type": "hotkey", "image": "static/manifest/data/task2-gpt5.4-mini-sample-3/24.webp", "action_value_1": ["ctrl c"], "thought": "刚才长命令又被截断了，我先中断当前输入，回到正常 shell 提示符，然后用分段方式写文件，避免单条命令太长。"}, {"id": 24, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/task2-gpt5.4-mini-sample-3/25.webp", "action_value_1": "cat > /home/user/Desktop/Case03_ThermalStep.mo <<", "thought": "终端已经回到正常提示符。现在我改成“逐行写入文件”的方式：先启动输出重定向，再一行行输入模型内容，最后用 `EOF` 结束，这样不会再被截断。"}, {"id": 25, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/task2-gpt5.4-mini-sample-3/26.webp", "action_value_1": "model Case03_ThermalStep", "thought": "现在 shell 正在等待文件内容。我按块输入模型文本，每块都不长，这样可以避免之前那种输入截断问题。"}, {"id": 26, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/task2-gpt5.4-mini-sample-3/27.webp"}, {"id": 27, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/task2-gpt5.4-mini-sample-3/28.webp", "action_value_1": "ls -l /home/user/Desktop/Case03_ThermalStep.mo", "thought": "模型文本已经写完并关闭。下一步我检查文件是否存在，然后在 OMEdit 里打开这个 `.mo` 文件进行仿真。"}, {"id": 28, "action_type": "wait", "image": "static/manifest/data/task2-gpt5.4-mini-sample-3/29.webp", "action_value_1": []}, {"id": 29, "action_type": "hotkey", "image": "static/manifest/data/task2-gpt5.4-mini-sample-3/30.webp", "action_value_1": ["enter"], "thought": "看起来命令行可能还没有真正回车执行，我直接补一个回车，让 shell 把刚才那条 `ls` 执行掉，然后确认文件是否存在。"}, {"id": 30, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/task2-gpt5.4-mini-sample-3/31